ygData.messageBody:
Well, I have to say that I liked the sig. I even passed it on to a few friends who chuckled at it.
And he has one point in the fact that it is at the bottom of he text. Might as well get upset at
OneList for their little "commerical" tagged on each and every email someone sends to the list.

But I WILL have to agree that the +ACI crap, (Which is why I included so much of the previous
comments in my reply) is annoying. (I even had to edit all that junk out when I forwarded it out.) I
understand it is probably something his mail program puts in and he/she has no idea that this junk
is in there. But it DOES get annoying. It's a shame that apparently it annoys people enough that
this email address is on a few kill lists.
